{"tid":1135550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我是記者 我的六四故事 5 月 5 日正式啓播","createTime":"2019-05-02T11:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T21:23:33.000Z","uid":37656,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be081b026b18157df86834c90bfaf01137640a33","tid":1135550,"uid":37656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"#計劃簡介 2019 年是「#六四」30 周年。30 年過去，不僅參與者暴亂惡名未洗刷、死難者沉冤未昭雪，更兼且當年事態日漸備受歪曲、或年輕人已無從瞭解事件經過。因此，當年曾身歷其境的記者，有責任將當日所見所聞、日後所思所感，再做一次紀錄，公諸於世，以為歷史見證。<br />\n⠀⠀<br />\n2018 年底，一批記者行家醞釀了這個再做紀錄的項目，得到香港記者協會的支持，並申請《#人民不會忘記》基金資助，分別以文字和影像來做記述。項目邀請得 30 位曾直接採訪「六四」的記者拍攝短片講述「#我的六四故事」；撰文者更達到 60 位，將會出版一本名為《#我是記者 六四印記》的書，2019年 6 月 4 日面世。<br />\n⠀⠀<br />\n經過半年多的籌劃，影片系列「我是記者－我的六四故事， I am a journalist, my June 4 story」將於 5 月 5 日正式啓播。<br />\n⠀⠀<br />\nYouTube 頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oPmbGRcDwJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoPmbGRcDwJg&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=8f2c118e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oPmbGRcDwJg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/iamajournalist64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fiamajournalist64%2F&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=01a94498\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/iamajournalist64/</a>"},{"pid":"c00d5a61e18c4d2c7725b03fba2c60223fefcd2e","tid":1135550,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0378819b76e6ee056e05e75ab9488bef48168b46","tid":1135550,"uid":37656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c00d5a61e18c4d2c7725b03fba2c60223fefcd2e","tid":1135550,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"就算7 80後都未必好清楚"},{"pid":"3c2931b9d3857630b66f3394ac79cadbbdc3cae2","tid":1135550,"uid":98795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:53:40.000Z","msg":"除左吾爾開希為慶祝就黎64而酒後駕駛, 唔知其他64領袖最近過成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94573c8ca679b64e645b5f3324bf8ff96523017","tid":1135550,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c00d5a61e18c4d2c7725b03fba2c60223fefcd2e","tid":1135550,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T11:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T21:23:33.000Z","msg":"2000－2002 呢一批人基本上都仲知道<br />\n<br />\n2009年我小學三年級嘅時候，常識堂老師同我哋講呢樣嘢， 因為內容太驚嚇，到落堂小息嘅時候個個嚇到面懵懵，全班靜默！<br />\n<br />\n 仲有 12年國教小六嗰陣時，班內同學仔個個都好激烈咁討論。<br />\n<br />\n利申：00後"}]}